{"tid":1417710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有無天水圍手足FC] 文化監暴何式凝叫人企定定比人拉","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T19:50:05.000Z","uid":149630,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03e847eb25e137ed3266c3e4aa994478a543564b","tid":1417710,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"喺舊登見到：<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7094816&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7094816%26page%3D1&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=9946497a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7094816&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCP5buf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCP5buf.png&h=a28e9184&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpZ1ufY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpZ1ufY.png&h=cc5d6d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泛民的秘密社運，大舉出擊。<br />\n<br />\n今早文化監暴何式凝在天水圍警局外，在黑警有攻擊舉動時，用咪誤導示威要企定不動，導致七十多人被捕。下午，黑警公佈兩個月來被捕義士數目。晚上，大量「文宣」，散佈謠言，指被捕人太多，要停止流水社運、游擊。再夾纏一堆運動影響經濟，會引起淺黃反感，所以要做返靜態的社運等等。<br />\n<br />\n文宣，是對外宣傳社運，對外解釋社運；當宣傳人員瘋狂地、大量地「分析」「人民」會反感，就是向人民宣傳他們應該要反感。這是策反，不是文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求face check </span></span>"},{"pid":"79129c5dba9d8783b0347dd0da96ef70280f69c9","tid":1417710,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"face check先"},{"pid":"416c767a3c2a9968e480ee7a6ff831b078c0dfd4","tid":1417710,"uid":31,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8ef8ea077fbd8c9a79f6f6fc5b766a7c54da0f","tid":1417710,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"如果FC完真有此事真係要好好咁同佢理論吓喎,唔好再俾佢送啲手足去死喎,我真係唔明坐係度比狗拉有咩用,痴撚線"},{"pid":"912e75b05f48366ae3cd4598ba6aff8e9ebdbe21","tid":1417710,"uid":66221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"唔係以為肯比狗拉人地會善待你呀"},{"pid":"b72300187efa11aca85fa2d76daa0f82a5c5a4ab","tid":1417710,"uid":201374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"哩啲唔撚係和理非,係左膠"},{"pid":"43e7158efce7c23cc78536f576fc46ccad9e059c","tid":1417710,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongshield\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongshield&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=3759a2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongshield</a><br />\n<br />\n上去問"},{"pid":"f4516987e36b7c2eb3be1032bb23f8a8ba23a5df","tid":1417710,"uid":261986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"(長文) 是勇武太快？定和理非太慢？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417762</a>"},{"pid":"82e35af6ac9a74601f83bd33fc97a6fca592df30","tid":1417710,"uid":261435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">暫時係睇到37:00 市民開始叫「黑社會」，何式凝宣布Live結束，此事黑警開始衝出去，市民逃走。<br />\n<br />\n聽唔到有叫人唔好郁俾人拉。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157093959730306&amp;id=664820305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157093959730306%26id%3D664820305&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=b310a6bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157093959730306&amp;id=664820305</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"9d9e4a48148c423005a312191830c51adaf4a889","tid":1417710,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:32:20.000Z","msg":"當黑警放催淚彈個陣，何式凝同黑警講我呢邊無扔石，係個邊（手足）扔，要放催淚彈就放個邊。<br />\n<br />\n當防暴有行動時，何式凝叫手足唔好郁，企起到，做返和平遊行集會。最後黑警拉晒89個手足，唯獨無拉何式凝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2450f656609b800367e1bf3ee249a68491c1fb2c","tid":1417710,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:39:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"769d66ba147aa96a285f2945aa6fff1c940e4cba","tid":1417710,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:49:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46dc657b026f4fadba976a5dc6163ce00d2a005","tid":1417710,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:50:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}